{"tid":1504112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[點解麗晶保安咁惡] 瑞安集團起底，梁振英、廖長江辦公室都喺瑞安","createTime":"2019-08-25T08:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:15:28.000Z","uid":276716,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1c99440fc9c49531efaa32c0d8ac1730c155ef7e","tid":1504112,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"瑞安物業管理係屬於瑞安集團。老闆係羅康瑞，同梁振英關係密切。集團係中國有大量投資項目。<br />\n<br />\n第一個支持689的富豪<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190507/2_668239_0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F2_668239_0%2F&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=3a6d7ce6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F2_668239_0%2F&h=8b8532c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190507/2_668239_0/</a><br />\n<br />\n集團總部位於<span style=\"color: red;\">灣仔瑞安中心</span>，喺稅務大樓隔離。<br />\n<br />\n瑞安中心二樓目前係<span style=\"color: red;\">入境處租用做更換智能(監控)身分證嘅換領中心</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">梁振英</span>擔任主席嘅一帶一路國際合作香港中心有限公司、大灣區香港中心有限公司嘅地址都係瑞安中心九樓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X9m6eXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX9m6eXu.jpg&h=add6d9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而「建制」派召集人<span style=\"color: red;\">廖長江</span>大律師嘅辦事處位於瑞安中心十一樓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxEWBVo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxEWBVo.jpg&h=54e2ec71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日係冇人辦公，有需要聯絡佢地請work day先揾。"},{"pid":"77fed9566152c29ae32e19448d5c7c16d674944b","tid":1504112,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"777ae5eaa2bab68b68bc1147ad1bfad84284ffeb","tid":1504112,"uid":8441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:12:33.000Z","msg":"CY選前 做緊瑞安非執董<br />\n<br />\n梁振英辭 瑞安房地產非執董<br />\n 政治版 2011/12/31  <br />\n瑞安房地產（00272）昨宣布，梁振英辭任集團非執行董事職務，今日起生效。通告指，梁振英請辭是因為要專注特首選舉工作，並確認與董事會沒有意見分歧。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英早前已陸續辭去商業機構的非執董職務，包括星島新聞集團非執行董事，本月17日已生效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/755477/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E8%BE%AD%20%E7%91%9E%E5%AE%89%E6%88%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E9%9D%9E%E5%9F%B7%E8%91%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F755477%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25BE%25AD%2520%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%2591%25A3&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=37561d39\" target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/755477/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E8%BE%AD%20%E7%91%9E%E5%AE%89%E6%88%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E9%9D%9E%E5%9F%B7%E8%91%A3</a>"},{"pid":"16eff9c5b277f0d619c44b4ca80930a004a91e0f","tid":1504112,"uid":159002,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:32:23.000Z","msg":"推 用瑞安物管既屋苑<br />\n求起底update<br />\n<br />\n麗晶花園（觀塘）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propertyType=2&amp;id=3125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fglobal-elements%2Festate-locator%2Fdetail.html%3FpropertyType%3D2%26id%3D3125&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=f5f56743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propertyType=2&amp;id=3125</a><br />\n<br />\n天頌苑（天水圍）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propertyType=2&amp;id=3032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fglobal-elements%2Festate-locator%2Fdetail.html%3F