s://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fglobal-elements%2Festate-locator%2Fdetail.html%3FpropertyType%3D2%26id%3D3109&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=d7f28971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propertyType=2&amp;id=3109</a><br />\n<br />\n洪福邨（元朗）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propId=1&amp;estId=2776&amp;dist=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fglobal-elements%2Festate-locator%2Fdetail.html%3FpropId%3D1%26estId%3D2776%26dist%3D1&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=bd84a8f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propId=1&amp;estId=2776&amp;dist=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商場：<br />\n南山邨商場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propertyType=1&amp;id=2761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fglobal-elements%2Festate-locator%2Fdetail.html%3FpropertyType%3D1%26id%3D2761&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=497715c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/global-elements/estate-locator/detail.html?propertyType=1&amp;id=2761</a>"},{"pid":"957c840e56f44cff179fdd5225ac5ce07b43bc9e","tid":1504112,"uid":186431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"原來咁猛底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b382c125c36dc1698ed927955dbfba8b493ed6d","tid":1504112,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"麗晶本身都係瑞安建築起 即係應該咁當年都無換過物管 唔知有冇黑幕呢"},{"pid":"79f0a671e6b2b1198704f4296